com.knitting.jamacoi
Class Report_Regression_Results

java.lang.Object
  com.knitting.jamacoi.Report_Regression_Results

public class Report_Regression_Results
extends java.lang.Object

This class implements usable and more meaningful reports that the Regression class has calculated. These reports have standard formating with every field labled. The class can be replaced or overridden to provide custom reporting. This class provides the important function of separating the calculation of regression results from the reporting of these results. This keeps the Regression class smaller and more understandable.
